metadata.name: Circle of Light
metadata.description:
Delhi's bussiest Metro station and one of the biggest shopping hub of the city Delhi, Rajiv Chowk also known as The Connaught Place. This place is located in the heard of capital city of India. Its the major hangout junction for youth of city and also stormed with local and international tourists.
This drone shot is taken back in 2018 from the height of 500M.


Clicked by Mayank Tiwari 
A travel and landscape content creator from India exploring the world. I love to shoot emotions of people and Nature.

This is 1/1 Edition
